  const handleMainCategory = (category) => {
    const newMain = selectedMainCategory === category ? null : category;
    setSelectedMainCategory(newMain);
    setSelectedSubCategory(null);
    if (newMain) {
      navigate(`?main=${encodeURIComponent(newMain)}`);
    } else {
      navigate("");
    }
  };

  const handleSubCategory = (subName) => {
    const newSub = selectedSubCategory === subName ? null : subName;
    setSelectedSubCategory(newSub);
    const main = selectedMainCategory;
    if (newSub) {
      navigate(
        `?main=${encodeURIComponent(main)}&sub=${encodeURIComponent(newSub)}`
      );
    } else {
      navigate(`?main=${encodeURIComponent(main)}`);
    }
  };

  // Sync with URL on load
  useEffect(() => {
    const query = new URLSearchParams(location.search);
    const main = query.get("main");
    const sub = query.get("sub");

    if (main && mainCategories.includes(main)) {
      setSelectedMainCategory(main);
    }
    if (main && sub && subCategories[main]?.some((s) => s.name === sub)) {
      setSelectedSubCategory(sub);
    }
  }, [location.search]);

  return (
    <div>
      <Navbar />
      <div className="container">
        <h1>AP TG Center Records</h1>
        <div className="main-buttons">
          {mainCategories.map((category) => (
            <div key={category} className="main-button">
              <button
                onClick={() => handleMainCategory(category)}
                className={`category-btn ${
                  selectedMainCategory === category ? "selected" : ""
                }`}
              >
                {category}
              </button>
              {selectedMainCategory === category && (
                <div className="sub-buttons">
                  {subCategories[category]?.map((sub) => (
                    <button
                      key={sub.name}
                      onClick={() => handleSubCategory(sub.name)}
                      className={`sub-category-btn ${
                        selectedSubCategory === sub.name ? "selected" : ""
                      }`}
                    >
                      {sub.name}
                    </button>
                  ))}
                </div>
              )}
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        {selectedSubCategory && topGrossers[selectedSubCategory] && (
          <div className="grossers-content">
            <table className="grossers-table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th colSpan="2">
                    {
                      subCategories[selectedMainCategory]?.find(
                        (sub) => sub.name === selectedSubCategory
                      )?.content
                    }
                  </th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <th>Movie</th>
                  <th>Gross</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                {topGrossers[selectedSubCategory].map((movie, index) => (
                  <tr key={index}>
                    <td>{movie.name}</td>
                    <td>{movie.gross}</td>
                  </tr>
                ))}
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        )}
      </div>
    </div>
